p[speak]:The Builder Academy is foremost a training academy for anyone willing to learn or teach how to build a virtual World. Due to our success and the stagnation of the CircleMUD codebase we have also released our code for anyone desiring a stable and functional codebase. tbaMUD is the continued development of the codebase formerly known as CircleMUD.

p[speak]:And we use it to mean both the Academy for training, and the codebase that is made freely available to the community. The most challenging aspect of running a mud is finding good builders. You will hear this from the admin of every MUD that has ever been.

